div.head: January
div.ab: Re sil dalach doine toided in ri remain luid fo recht nard nerain crist hi kł enair
Essodir intepscop abb ecailse airde manchene an airgge scoithine mind mairce
Marmartra rodanis conachleir caineisce findlug cofeib huasle fintan derb duin bleisc
Bas caith acquilini combuidin ba balcu hifuil cristtreachurpu docoemnagtar tlactu
Togairm semeon srotha cocrist cruth ronglea bacaingrian greit nua ciar igen duibrea
Raith corig rantoga iulian ba haill nglaine nidlig sar slan suba baithis mar meicc maire
Martra luciani coslog mar ba dixu imrordus ashuasliu tosach corguis issu
Etsecht egimoni epscop etla arda ercnat hua an orbba nechtan nair dealba
Ailli geill cenglaini argnuis rig roradis fælan deoda digrais felix finn uitalis
Almini anitge arnanteccma drochrann milit caid cain cathbarr diarmait inse clothrann
Croch in martir phetar cosintluag lan gaile ahegept an suba tanic macc mar maire
Martra mar muscenti conachleir chain chlannaich críst asruna rinnaid laicenn macc baith bannaich
Ambennacht ronbia balc itge cenalgais sulpicc sothnge suabais clair abb pichtadis
Pais gluceri deochain diarfiadait basercach sruth nola noeb sochlach felix fland find fechtnach
Foraith mur mór ngalar carais mortromtredan ingrian ban ban muman ite cluana credail
Craidbig hifeil fursa fris rocobsat rige noi mili meith buada forfichit mar mile
Nosmolammar menic fobi nidatcalaid lucht cessais cenchinaid hifeil antoin manaigh
Morad petair epstail hiroim rad asdixu lasinlith ashuasliu tasc mar mathair issu
Etsecht maire marthæ coinugum nodnali lasinfeil cosaire senphol cain conani
An cethrur conuagu foroenlith as noebu molocca moecca sabbaist ocus oenu
Robat oin dampnadud comrig reim as dixu fainche feim as huasliu agna ingen issu
Etsecht ingen comgaill colman macc huibeona ualerius cendigna felix fuair cuairt ceolda
Cesad seueriani clemati consadu ronsnadat dondrigu conandunud danu
Dommanmain domchorpan ropmur arcech merblen babaill bruth oir orlan conatriur deiblen
Nidedbul alláithe lith friscuirter gretha cocrist cechaing saithi pol im bathis bretha
ISbrigach asluagad larig dodanfarchi sluag orta iargortai lapais policarpi
Carais mæda muirgein mirbuil gein combuadaib bert glanbuaid fiadrigaib agnetis doichnuagaib
La haccobran huanni pais ocht nuag conani gabsat buaid condirgi sluag mar mesorani
Ain epscoip roradius ronsnadat diarndilius hipolitus paulus gillas constantinus
Sesca archet martir martra morsus doros ainsium arlin amus enan rois rind solos
Sluind æd fortren ferna mæl anfaid ainm remain benait conrig romoir barr find forsluag enair

div.head: February
div.ab: Morait kł febrai fros martir mar ngledenn brigit ban balc nualann cend caid caillech nerenn
Airitiu meic maire hitempul derb dímais sluag mar martir suabais lafindig nduirn ndigrais
Donroemat colane dogres arachtrogi sluagad find cofeli felicis simfroni
Fronius is magnus gelaisa roffesor german martir huasal cuanda credal cresen
Crotha corp agatha ingerat conglaini la issu coṅgili tathus mar maith airi
Andreas ard a ordan epscop mel mind rigi lucia conani nadchumscaigset mili
Mellan inse huaisle macc huichuinn nadnale lomman locharn brige locha huair ard age
Hua an indeciss ba imchrist alabra fiachra ba fer ferda ab hirard amra
Mochuaroc indecnai noeb nadamair digna cairech dergan deoda epscop ronan rigda
Retlu chain gein mbuada bruth oir etrocht age cronan caid cendigna grian gel glasse mare
Mogopnat coṅglanbuil imṡeirc crístbahilmain maith leiss gres diagarmaim epscop etchen inmain
IMmonepscop simplex slechta primslog promtha daman mil mind martra comacraid chain chrochtha
Hicurchan modomnoc anair darmuir ngledend dobert brigach nualann sil mbuach mbec nerenn
Hiroi ualentini marcellus roringed hiflaith crist roclannad ochtmoga caincinged
Cain celebrad domnaig iarnabarach ndadaig. lacesaid sloig brigaig buaid meic de dianamaid
Donduaig iuliana annainm nel cohimbel laisceith scél ahannaig demon damail indel
Dlomthus cach cohollmuir feil cormaicc conglanboil lafeil fintain filich cluana edhnig adboil
Bebais incaid colman molipa nodnali hifeil fir connoebi rutuli siluani
Sluind lett lapais pupli pais maircill mind mbuadach boethini mor mainech macc caindelda cuanach
Gaius intepscop achesad nicelar immaslecht scel ndogar fiche trénar trebar
Togairm fintain choraig post contemptum mundi hifeil fir colainni uiruli iocundi
INantoig ahortan petair adfet ecna gein lurint lanfrecra lafeil toidlig thecla
Mathias intapstal arcrist cesais riaga dondrichiud ronsnada conneoch adidṅgialla
Lapais luciani cruimther crochtha demna abb iæ an ergna cummini find febda
Fofrid cenn poil apstail indanchinged chredlaig hifeil indḟ̇ir chumrig teolis treoin trednaig
Togairm alaxandri hisosad sanctorum foroenlith lantene gene darcellorum
Lacessad habundi marolaidib lammais feil congain cing innis airec cinn iohannis
Hifeil sillain bendchoir deich nóebuaga delbdai la cessad sluaig ḟerdai forcennat crich febrai

div.head: March
div.ab: For kł mis marta nitmordai frianguidi senan moinen moysi dabid cille mune
Mamemraigter feli hipais lucilia gein senphoil slan doe feil find fergna ia
Hipais floriani fail daretlainn remain cele críst cain erail moachru mac senan
Sluinn cesad indepscoip hiroim rigda cainlech cosluag adbul ainglech lucius les lainrech
Roleblaing nibalbda aclu darsal sairde carthach rigda ruamach ciaran sluagach saigre
Ronsnadat iarleri delaith de for dirgi sluag orta conani hi féil uictorini
INmain decheng deoda nadlig diarnduain digna felicitas noebda perpetua primda
Senan inse cathaig crothais ecrait narach connadail cli buadach epscop beoæd bagach
Bas cethracat miled comorsluag basorchu diaduarcaib frihilchu grian hilucc dub dorchu
Dorograd cohangliu constantin cain cainlech lassafrith eo ainglech carann cruiche inchomded
ITcoimti arfiadat isindlaith huasḟlaithib liberen senan suthain constantin ri rathin
Reairichtain aḟerainn ar críst crochais colainn intorgan chet buada grigoir ruama rolainn
Ronsnada mochoemoc donbithchoemnu bias cuangus caid cosoas oliath mor maith dias
Dionis intepscop ata cliara coema comainn crist ronsnada saluator ronsoera
Sern iacob ordan lucas lir huas trilis frichríst carsat sanais meicc nessan ondinis
INmain acht lademon eugenia fordumun abban doss oir ainglech finan lainrech lobur
Lassar greine ane apstal herenn huaige patraic comeit mile rop ditin artruaige
Comorbuidin martra nabdar ili lochta latiamda rorimed sesca miled mochta
Molachtoc lagrigoir ingradgreit asdixu ioseph ainm as huasliu aite alainn issu
Etsecht policroni noibepscoip aschadu cechain ceim as dirgiu comorsluag badanu
Donbith ba mor mbuada benedicht balcc age foroenlith ler slúagda ennæ airdirc airne
Ardchesad secundi cenambriathraib bia balc les lir dardoe failbe anle ia
Ingen dalach dærmar feradaig asarddam ocrist adfet orddan mo medoc mind nalban
An lanamain liagach frisnaig etla ainbech scire cain car tredan mochta credal craidbech
Crochad ocus chompart issu críst itcori foroenlith coleri lapais iacobi
Hiletha dorochair mochelloc iarlaithib feil intinchill ṡuthain cille aidbile achid
Hisex kł aperil iartuaslucud anman asreracht scel ndermar issu abru thalman
Donrogra ronsoera sechphiana ronṡena maria ronmora inmor magdalena
Lalith ingen mbaiti bas sluaig mair cofeili hifeil fir conhuagi grigoir nazareni
Sluind mochua balla blog conordun ainbich colman olinn ligaig la feil tolai craidbith
Croch ninach annissi cocleir bain badaithiu dober barr treabithu martai forsluaig saithiu

div.head: April
div.ab: Soerait kł april ambrois comeit glaine congaib as mo suba feil de feilib maire
Morsluag amphiani diambu domun dubach drebraing iar cath chalad issin síth soer subach
Sluag euagair huasail asrola asæth setaib cethracha derigaib ardib cainib cetaib
Cain tigernach credal arcrist cechmbais mbreuis as mbruchta sruam sois cluana alle heuis
Hifeil mair meiccula beccain coṁbuaid lere bathess phatraicc primda adrannad inhere
Erenius intepscop ata mor a mile bacain doss conuaigi hifiadit find fine
Finan camm cinn etich immaib marndelma bagerait crist chainde osleib bledach bledma
Bas enair inmartir bamor tuire tempuil nírærad riamuntir cenn failad abb bennchoir
Buaid secht noebuaig nennacc incechthreib asrati asafuil nadibdai lafeil cain quadrati
Croch appolloin cruimthir arcrist coemtar folaid oross eo ainm subaid cuanda rigda romaid
Ronain moedoc mainech aris brathair bagach hua acht ronoebad do dunlang derb dalach
Dalais ansa opair crist fri crucha cretair iuil epscop abb popuil sab soer suidephetair
Conaprimluag sona argabeoil cech gena geraitcristcain dechoid pol dechoin donrena
INrigepscop tassach dobert odonanaicc corp crist indrig firbailcc lacommain dophatricc
Primda breo nad aithbi arfig tola tothlai ba cain lia luagmar ruadan locharn lothrai
La carissa rigda asaruamda relicc doreith duit forsidit feil indechoin felicc
Lafeil petair deochoin drebraing martra mbuade conachleir cain dine donnan ega huare
Arfeit hifeil septim soerdechoin dodidnad laisren lassar buadach abb leithglinne ligach
Luid ermogin airdirc iarforbu agliad cohissu an soad asuacht chorpan chriad
Lacesad eradi cruimther crochtha tuile feil hiruaim ran mbale noeb naeorpa huile
INalbain conglaine iarlecu cechṡubai luid huan conamathair armbrathair merubai
Ronain pilip apstal asaidbliu cechthredan diannainm arruin athar gin locharna lethan
Lochet epscop ibair asrort cenn cech herais an breo huastuinn trilis inherinn bicc bebais
Buaid na tri macc nennacc hisurn sochla dine pais giurgi grian buada cotrichait mor mile
Marc huasal inegept nadlig foccul faille flesc oir adbul tinne epscop mor macc caille
Cirillus cain cimmid cessais roi rinne dochrist cachaind aille cosluag adbul imbe
IMmacurtis angil acarcraib ceatesed alaxander huasal abb roma incresen
Cristofor la cronan rois chree cotalci inafeil cen sotlai luid mor miled martrai
Martra germain chruimthir crist bamor atiachra coningen cain huaitne foroenlith lafiachra
Forcennat cleir napril olisleir dorrimi ronan lethrois huamni hirroim croch cirini

div.head: May
div.ab: Kł mai nethchoimi gein pilipp asdixu and tinscan as huaisliu praicept alaind issu
Escomlud saturnin cocrist immeranicc la etsecht iarsirchnet nechtain daltai patraicc
Primairecc craind cruiche crist conilur buada bas conlaid cain age feil mar maire huaga
Hipais anateiri mochua cain deochoid macc cuinneni chlothaig hi feil siluain dechoin
INdechoin eutimus lahelair sechphiana lotar laithi litha frisrocaib arfiada
Fer roscrib centarcai cainscela crist crochthai admuinter laflaithi gein mor matha mochtai
Mochiaroc labreccan digerait atglainiu carsat crist as diliu in echdromma dairiu
Uictor ocus maxim imcrist cotaruicset arserc rig rocarsat inaḟuil fotruicset
Failsigud mor micheil donbith bascel promtha pais cirill cain cartha epscop santan sochla
Hi sithlaith indaltair imbi torm cechtempuil ronsnada insluagach comgall buadach bennchuir
Buaid nioib cendermat dorig nel bafordorcc mochritoc cain munter ocus cruimther cormacc
Cyriacus crochtha trichetaib donascnai ailitheir ainm coemda la heirc noebda nascai
Noebmuinter teraci probique iarsetaib iarserbchrochaib siraib sesiur ar se cetaib
Corona is uictor conacleir cenmathim foroenlith ler suthain feil cain carthaig raithin
Rath in spirta sechtai senaig forcleir ngelbain tiamda saran saidbir feil duiblitir dermair
Togairm brenainn chluana isin mbithlaith mbuadig bas caid carnig firbailc la feil áin hui suanaig
Sluagad adrionis uictoris bassillæ scorsit cenchuit fainne fordinn flatha finne
Feil mairc maith rorigad momedoc mór mainech modomnoc mind mbuadach feil brain bicc ochloenad
Cliara urbain glana nisgignetar tola ananmann itgela trebroenan afola
Fuil mór marcellossæ luid fothalmain tassi foroenlith itgessi gerbassi ⁊protassi
Tiamda martir mirbuil morderin dede thurinn colman lobur rolainn barrinn dromma culinn
Cechaing animm ronain find forriched rinnach lasinfer cain clannach baitheni mac finnach
Findsluag epecthiti as danu as daingniu iarcesad lahingru frisindled lahaingliu
Augustin intepscop ermes abb mor mile colman inmain age aidbe tuathach tire
Toticc feil iohannis inmain age huage dionis derb dana dunchad ia huare
Aritiu choir cholmain stellam sluind cenladna beccan carais figle hicluain aird aadba
Acolius cruimther conachleir as noebu aḟuil fiad cech diniu dorortad foroenu
Ronsnada cohaingliu inmain sonmech sathe german grian arsruithi aite phatraic mache
Morṡluag pullionis ronsnada dondrindnibm lacummain conglanbail ingen allen inmain
Noebapstal arfiadat hifudamnaib ecnai gein tomais cenopni hifudamnaib ecnai
Cesad crisogini lapais paternelle mi mai comeit mile daprimfeil fortnedæ

div.head: June
div.ab: Oid menman feil tecla ardlig din achetal cosluag adbul huasal hikł iuin etan
Erasmus intepscop anbreo combruth brige bert cocríst cleir ṁbuada trichet molthach mile
Mil críst hicrich nerend ard nainm tartuinn tredan coemgen caid cain cathar oglinn dalind lethan
Luid apollinaris doḟlaith de fordirgi conachleir conuagi latarmrith martini
Martra marciani morsus ilar mbuada aill feir moir maith dine aill ingena huaga
Huagcesad amanti morgnim mafolugai mæl aithchen conglanbeil luid fothalmain tugai
Togairm poil inmartir iarmorgnim cotalcai feil coluim cenṡotlai inmormeicc huiartai
Airitiu indnoeib ioib iarmbuaid ocus banchad feil medran mor ndidnad feil murchon comarath
Ronsnadat don bithlaith imbithbi les lainrech boethene ard ainglech columcille caindlecl
Condrecat forenchoi cenmair dodafarnaic primḟeil mairc mind nardircc lafeil mbuadaich barnaibb
Basilla inbuadach bretha huan hifailti feil meicc thail indnoebdai lapais furtunati
Feil incredail chæmain diansantlethanslonnad torocnnan buan bannach darleir lethan longach
Labartholoin primda itmeirb manichuala cechaing huan coriga mac nissi caid cluana
Condreccat diblinaib foroenlith ler sluagach nem mac huibirn brigaig labenedicht mbuadach
Bendacht forsingerait carais crist cofirbuil lasluid slog commorgail uictus maccan mirbuil
Mogerait ingiricc immaslecht sluag sobail nifrith set na samail dó domaccaib domain
INdoss oir oschrichaib ingrian án huastuathaib congreit rig balcc brathair cain míl moling luachair
Laboethan finn fechtnach furuthran cofegi meicc moenain conuagi o lainn liagaig leri
Luid afuil foroenu fiadsluagaib combraissi dorig batir huissi gerbassi protassi
Pais poil ciriaci cosindunud marsin fælan cosinbuaidsin intamlabar ansin
Ainle sochla sluagach frismbrucht ammuir inlach cormacc bacain clerech hua lithan inligach
Laiacob nalphei danocht cetcliar ngelda feil fir nadchar corplen cronan fortren feran
Foraithmet mochoe nifail ardonsela insab socla sona onaendruim donrema
Riggein iohain babtaist masuleir ronfeithiss latathcor cenaithis iohain meicc do effeiss
Feil sinchill feil telle batir crend arda lamluoc glangelda grian liis moir dealba
ISadabal acesad apais olrostaurus caingrian gallicanus iohannis is paulus
Ropromtha trmartra ata morthruim threthain secht nderbrathir caithir hiruann letha lethain
Hillecoin moir mide cruimmene conani foroenlith colleire paiss find fabiani
Feil poil ocus phetair conaidbli angretha nistarcai deilm catha feil forbruinnib betha
Buaid soli istiamdai tamtiu ioib inmain benait glass find fothmein forsluagad iuin ilmain

div.head: July
div.ab: Iuil hikł mirbuil mare maras matha bas naroin seirb sruithe simon ocus tatha
Taimthiu eutaicc epscoip damassi conani pais processi rigdai riag mar martiani
Martra cirionis críst nihattach mbelle tarmbreth tomaiss aille feil digraiss dartinne
Dagordan mór martain marosellaib soimle lacet martir namra finnbarr inse doimle
Donmartir agatho conacleir cain comul roir críst síd slemon amorṡeircc laomun
Moninne intṡleibe cuilinn bacain age gobais buaid geil glaine siur maire mare
Lamorṡluagad ligmar parmeni trom toiden mæl ruain adreth richeth grian án inse goidel
Gabais brocan scribuid soerbuaith cennachtuisel ladiarmait derb lassar grian ġel glinne huissen
Asslonnud an onchon mosticc cach nodnali fricríst caraiss lere garban can cind sali
Sluind cesad sechtbrathar diambu croch crist carcar cuan marcc mar sostan dase mile martar
Lamartra narigna eufemia slogda benedicht balcc age macc craibdech conlocha
Conruala cohaingliu nazair scel cechsenaid felix bamaitulaid conasluag mor melaid
Milis ainm conani euangeli noebdai lamsiloc donrigraid luid hisidlaith soerdai
Ronsnada intepscop iacob as næbem atneocham nonalem condechenbur noiden
INda apstal deac dofarcat cechnarim fosdail reasluag dirim issu foṡil adaim
Doticfa cechdia docrist acht coentis itge cosluag suabais inmaccain mammetis
Ronmorat anitgi horum atque harum cechmartir adrimem forsluag scillitarum
Sluagad innarigna snaidsium insith soerda comorfesiur braithre inxpistina noebda
Noebitge sisinni itmerb mainfrescai taricc eim fritoscai comorbuidin brestai
ITbrestai inbainmeicc sabina soer ainbech indromula ruamach lacuriphin craibdech
Croch ard heli martir moraid relicc lechtaig coningenraid tuchtaig pais fraxidis fechtnaig
Findgein magdalena maire mind cechdunaid pais apolnair huasail mobiu inse cuscraid
Lacesad uincenti cocrist cechaing saithe hiruaim bareim sruithe danoi miled maithe
Madail duit ahere dotchobair cing bage tathut cenn cheit mile declan arde máre
Mocholmoc moṡiloc lanessan dialammais iacob cing innis bas brathar iohannis
Hipais iouiani conacleir cain glanoir tarmchruthad iarndedoil issu hisleib thaboir
Taimthiu semioin manaig bamorgrian dontalmain lacesad sluaig inmain inantuaig aird adbail
ISadbul acobair conaṡluagud chaindlech teophil tor óir ainglech pantaleo laindrech
Lupus ocus simplicc epscoip cenchuit ndigna prosper cocleir huagda naretlanna rigda
Recht crist nodocantais corunaib attgleintis lasluag nafrith anfot abdon ocus sennis
Sluag iuil comeit mile fortniada ard age epscop an ahere colman mac darane

div.head: August
div.ab: Do kł inauguist doraraicc mór mbrige lafeil macc mochaba ochtmoga mór mile
Lasinmathair marsin teothota inbaidsin lotar forsinbuaidsin natri maccain maithsin
Metrapoil indeoin derbiled conani inairecht connoebi corpan soer stefani
Bid failid iarrichtu frimm ismor adocha indoebgerait rigda molua macc ocha
Cesad an herenti ardlig comarcc coemda la hosualt noeb nailme airdri sachsan soerda
Sistán epscop ruamach rucc suas saithe snamach lamchua cli buadach ocluain dolcain dalach
Dlom coic arthrib coectaib blíadan brig ronfeitheiss morfessiur cen aithiss conattail ineffiss
Feil beoan meicc nessain noll ni hattach mbille colman epscop aille oinis bo finne
Feith latt pais antoni firmi fortren muinter inachud cain chlaintair nathi credal cruimther
Croch lan lurint dechoin diachorpan bacalad lasluag slan soer sodad blaan cain chinngarad
Guid airennan eccnai assaclu nadchelar laualeran nidan triburtius tren trebair
Togairm laissren inse muredaig moir mochtai cocleir moir nadaithbi feil segeni sochlai
Hipolitus martir bamirbuil athoiden cosluag adbul huasal momedoc mind goidel
Lagairm furtunati darfairce ler longach mac intair cain cingid feil fachtnai maicc mongach
IMorfeil ahaithmeicc firmathair arnathar cosluag rig ran clochar fer da chrich cain cathar
Lacroich adrionis cocreir nadchar dichmarcc feil maire mind nuagbailcc noebmathair morigmaicc
Rocess mammes martir morphian hicroich chalaid lacleir cain cenchinaid taimthiu teimnan manaig
Macc cresseni mernoc morais fiadait fairinn bafer raith diarturinn daig mor maith macc cairill
Croch inmartir magni cocleir combuaid blaithe mochta mor maith sithbe enan dromma raithe
Rochess diascorus arcrist cing asferdu pampil breo asamru commorsluag bageldu
Guid hifeil uincenti dochongnam fritainmain epscop senac sulbair cluana hiraird adbail
Attaig itge tiamdai daltai poil conani guid maccraith conoebi indnoib emiliani
Lapais furtunati immaluid lin catha foroenlith luad mbetha feil eogain aird sratha
Lasreith sluaig stenoni ascela roclotha senphatraicc cing catha coemaite arsrotha
Rosreth scel achesta cechleth cosal sruamach iarmorhroich rorigad inbartholom buadach
Buaid pais quinti martir diachelebrad comeir fornem cosluag roreil rorebraing iarndrobeil
Drong inmartir glandai ruffi cain combinni corig nel noeb ndoe luid tre rore rinni
Ronain ciriacus conachleir cain chathlaicc hermes cessais rochneit intairdirc ahaffraicc
Asneid cesad eoin babtaist bith coleri lanoicet conhuagi forfresgabail heli
Alainn huag agappa asgrian dofornæbaib adreth buaid huasbuadaib conasethraib soeraib
Sernaitt eithre naugauist ædan ingrian gelda inse medcoit molma lapaulin nafedba

div.head: September
div.ab: For septimber kł cicilia condirgi cethri cet conuagi fiche lateor mile
Molatha teothota lasenan itsoerscom lacrist cain ambuaidseom conacleir itcoimseom
Colman dromma ferta longarad grian álaib mac nissi comilib ochonderib maraib
INmarlaith cenattail indatblaithe beccain agait mor amaccain imultan aird breccain
La brecbuaid turim dorograd ahere eolach caid cain age achid bo buaid lere
Lusca lamac cuilind caindecheng adrannai feil sceithi slunn linni coluim roiss gil glannai
Glanchesad senoti assasoilsi slechta sluag anathais orta conilur a ferta
Foraithmentar maire nitmarbda fortercfit latiamda iarṡetaib cotribcetaib martir
Mor lith linass cricha crothass longa luatha meicc intair tarriga feil cain ciarain chluana
Cli derggoir conglaini correcht tar sal sidi sui dianseriu ninmall finnbarr maige bili
Pais prothi iacinthi ba conimbud galair sillan salm cech lobuir inimbliuch cain canair
Celebair feil nailbi lafleith sorcha snamaich hifeil laissren ligaig odaminis dalaig
Dlom diis arfichet martir comeit noebe lasincingid mbage dagan inbir doile
Dolling duit feil coemain bricc ladiis mbollmair pais caid cipriain ndermair lacesad cain cornail
La coissecrad mbaslicc maire mur cotalcai cirinus cenṡottlai luid cosluag mor martrai
Morthregeng nad dona moninn nuall cechgena ini laissren sona lalaissren mor mena
Eufemia cen digna riaid apaiss cinn bliadna broccan roiss tuircc tuirme lafeil romaith riagla
Rathatar hiriched secet miled mblaithe lagein cain cendigna enan dromma raithe
Raith conilur sochlach cocrist coemda taithlech cosluag rig ran remain enair inmain aithmet
Atneochain nahuaga doairset arndala indrigan daroma conaṡluag ronsnada
Snaidsiunn insab sluagach issansid nard noiblech ingrian gel colligdaid matha mur tren taidlech
Pantaleo muric ammorṡluag cateot secet cainsluag ooc ardib milib deacc
Doadmonan ia assatoidlech toiden roir issu huasal soerad mbuan mban goidel
Compert iohain huasail babtaist as mo scelaib acht issu dedoinib asamram ni genair
Lacleir iosebi soerais cechfleid forcraid do crist indḟir ṡercaig feil barre ochorcaig
Colman olaind alo lahuaigi alt legend combahe an nuallan iohain mar macc nerenn
Arndigerait chride a croch nipu arlius ronsnadat diarndilius cosmas damianus
Dofinnio gillæ itgessi cechcobair cliar mar marcill humail iunaill lalith labuir
Lagleo fridracc ndalach domichiel balcbuadach arsil nancrist nirach inmil slisgel sluagach
Septimber iarsaithib atsaigtis arseithir sui slan soithnge suthain cirine ban beithil

div.head: October
div.ab: Buaid prisci pais lucæ lith germain grian cetal feil noebreilce nuasal inochtimbir etan
Eleuther inmartir admuinter afeili onme foroenlini lapaiss iosebi
Soergein mairc inæggept asslonnud cech geno candida grian ṡona gein cain colmain elo
Ail marcellum nepscop conaidbli abriga lacesad nahuage inballgel baluina
Blog donnliic logmair laslóg martir namra sinech ingen ḟergnai cruachan maige abna
Abb cluana inlucell laboithene mbrigach fer dachrich cli buadach epscop luagach ligach
La matha mairc nepscop asrort sluag congainni lacleir cain cofinni feil cellaig collainni
Leicset luth conani arbrith aitrib rigi tret ingen conuagi lapais find faustini
Hifeil iosebi cechaing suas iarsetaib sluag dermar derigaib adeich artrib cetaib
Trichet arthrib dechib lafer cain centade fintan find fren fine dromma ingard age
ITana andirmann intrir immaradamni fortcenn lomman lainnech cainnech mac huidalann
Dlom fiac ocus fiachraig omni mor inmain sein mobi balc inbuaid sein inclarainech cain sein
Comgan ocus marcill collethet alinne indogrigan glanna feil findsige finne
Feil calisti epscop asneid for oenlini lacesad conuagi indepscoip paulini
Primchesad murorum roclos fonmbith mbuidnech damdatar mor dadlach iarserbcharcra cuimrech
Ciar tribcetaib cainib lahocht deich donbuaidsein riaguil raith arreimsein colman oncill ruaidsin
Roches mór inmartir necodimus nemda conachleir cain tuidme sab innarbba demna
Demin lapais pilipp primmartir donformaig trofimæ dontrednaig dobert crist cain cobraid
Ropcobair dun auster aschomart treriaga ronsnada ronsoera sluag suissi sechpiana
Pais eutaicc lafintan mældub mor ingairsin caingrian ocontleibsin denneoganacht ansin
Anbreo combruth aithri fintan firór promtha mac telchan tren trednach cathmil credlach crochda
Croch pilipp indepscoip lasrort sluag colleri matha mind cechrige lapais eusebi
Escomlud longini dondriglaith as dixu gegna gním as huaisliu toeban alainn issu
Asslonnud soer séuir isferr duit diansesser frisrocaib nem nuasal cocethrachait chresen
Condadeich dacoica lamaxim donascnai crist lafeil fir thuicsi laisren mór mac nascai
Nasad beoan mellan nachmod ataniam inmain cethrur coir feil ingen meicc iaair
Erc domnaig moir mainich abban abb caincliarach odran sab soer snamach colma hua fiachrach
ISfairsiung andalsom babilon aruamsom tatha ocus simon isdimor asluagsom
Sluag quinti commorbruth ronnain arcechngabud gabais buaid iarndilgud lataimthene talgud
Dacét sescat slane foroenlith connæbi hernach huag ardage colman macc huigaili
Quintinus cain crochtha fælan comeit meithle sernait cosluag aithre ochtimbir ardethre

div.head: November
div.ab: Lonan colman cronan conacleir gil grianaich sluaig helairderbdalaich soerat samain sianaig
Sruth apstal artire patraicc primda age dobert bendacht mbuada forercc arda slane
Sluinn elair darromuir murdebur mind senaid lith cain corcunutain lafeil coemain enaig
Inmain grian cenopni commorchleir ceneclai perpetua gen digra coniunx primda petrai
Pais domini airdirc immaslechta fermaicc doraith de bahorlan colman glinni delmaicc
Cedolegsad doine tremartra conani adreth riched ruanach dunad adriani
Drong adbul eusebi cerbogur aslige fofuair fortren toga tir mór himaig nime
Fornem nual cluadini luid cleir cain cenæra lalith linas tuatha barrinn mormaic æda
Donait ocus daman niptar ecnaid anbli foroenlith cosuilgi feil sinchi cosaidbri
Aed mac bricc dendrigraid becc nabumo ecaib isard isinmorlaith insab sil chuind chetaig
Corpbri cula raithin rath rigda corromuir sanctmartain soer samuil sliab oir iarthuir domuin
Doridnacht lasuithi soas comeit tiachrai dommchummain cain milte mac find fota fiachnai
For id eitsecht eutaicc martir maimrordaiss renotlaicc ard ergnuiss asneid init corgaiss
Clemeint ocus colman celebair afeile frigein crist conuagi tinscan lechsa leire
Lacesad secundi cosluagud cechdatha corgus mafutbotha tinscan greim dochatha
Cliar augustin epscoip dóig nochartais tredan troethais mór ngur ngalair cethrachait cain credal
Celebair feil tecla isíarmbuaid dorochair buaid beo buan balc athair laduilech cain clochair
Cain coisecrad eclass petair isphoil primdai meicc beraich conuagi feil reil ronain rigdai
Raid coisecrad mbaslicc iohain meicc cenmelacht luid cethracha ndillacht lamaxim mor ngerat
Guid escon lafroechan arbledma balc mbelaib lacesad corunaib sluag bassi hisnelaib
Noebdecheng conrualai cocrist lagein clemeint macc commain aharainn macc congraid ahereind
IArcesad himartrai mare loichet laindrech raith corigmacc nainglech cicilia cáin caindlech
Cesad cain clementis etertonnaib trethain adorthair achathir fotonnuib lir lethain
Laciannan doim liacc caindias diarturinn macc leneni rolainn la colman duib chuilinn
Lasinneoin caseon assaherchoin chorann luid achroich cainferann finchu obri gobann
Guid decheceng nderb ndalach copopul banbuadach banban bruth oir oiblech epscop siricc sruamach
Sruaim ecnai conani sechnall mind arflatha rogab ceol soer sodad molad patraic macha
Primtrecheng nachduthain trofini cenmaithim meicc bochrai buaid suthain oachud reid raitin
Rigfeil brenainn birra frismbruchta ler lebenn bacain mind mar ḟualang cenn find faithe nerend
Andreas asdanu frichroich ceim asuagu dobeir barr nodbagu nouimbir forsluagu

div.head: December
div.ab: Sluinn decimbir kł candida cain curach pais pancrati calad feil noib nesain ulad
Ollchesad pomeni iarserbgaibthib gorta gessi lalin martra mælodran mor mochta
Martra ard erachli conachleir indirdruin macc oigi conuagboil luaim liss moir mirbuil
Merobus cludicus conaidbli asreithe bahoen arsoer sruithi infial fer daleithe
Foraithmet iustini indepscoip conani amanti crispine umbani filadi
Feil gobbain gair mile cocleir martra mare mur ainglech abb huagi mac hui laindrech laine
Lapais policarpi conacleir soer sruamach omanistir mainich feil bain buti buadaig
Buaid hichtbrichtain humail donarlaid darromuir docrist cachaing figil hicurchan cenchodail
Cadlai indiingein aillela nadchlithi iscain sluag allaithi digrein airthir liphi
Ladacoicat ogda cethracha colani lalith capitolini feil modimoc dani
Damassus lamṡenoc mugnai tuathmaig lethan feil meltoc cain cathair cosluag tren dartrethain
Tor oir huas cech lermaig gebaid coir frimanmain finnian finn frem inmain cluana hiraird adbail
Arlaithi ndil ndalach tairset comeit mile boethan cluana credlach colum trednach tire
Donrogra dondriglaith rig roucc arsiur saph caid cloithi caor drursus conathriur
Togairm fausti fechtnaig cosluagud atempuir lafeil flainn fial impir comarba buain bennchuir
Buaid finn ualentini cocleir cain atroeroiss feil mophioc digraiss card chainnlech camroiss
Ronsnada sluag uictoir iarmbuaid gnima gaile corisamm ánsuba issu mór macc maire
Mórgrian innaclannsa magniu maith amminnsa diucaill dian anammsa ropat failte frimsa
Frimanmain ropfailid conimmud aslogaid cain glanmainn de dulig samdann cluana bronaig
Barigach hiarleri sluag mar immerádi reta huan forceti hicoemthecht ignáti
ITge indnoib thomais atneochain reabannaib abas bascel ningir inindie hiarrannaib
Ronnain itge tuæ itharnaisc nadlabrai lahemene ngelda debrú berba balbai
Pais ochtcet cain martra cosescait soer slechta lamthemnioc donrigraid cluana firmaith ferta
Fresdal luciani lamchua cain coclait macc lonain donteiccmaicc indadaig renotlaicc
INnotlaicc mór mirbuil crist omaire bagaig genair ladith ndorca ri sorcha sil adaim
Atneochain diarndigde mochommóc conani caingrian guires mile ainm sorcha stefani
Slanchotlu iohannis ineffis án bortgal abrathair asarddam laiacob nordan
Airdirc annuall suthain sechcach coemda methil cantais duais dianathair inmaccradain o
Bidemid acobair incechuair donnecrai uictor cosluag sochla laheleran necnai

Ecen charcra crochais cliar mar mansueti lahelbi conuaigi arriccfamm aḟeli
